value: The position of government organizations on the project of main E40 waterway restoration
06.2016, UN Minutes of an Environmental Council meeting

We collected documents on the E40 waterway project which are available for public use, e. g. brochures, various feasibility studies and an environmental assessment of the project. Also here you can find 17 responses from various state institutions of Belarus to the official inquiries of an NGO "Bahna" about their position on the route arrangement project.
Documents provided on the E40 waterway restoration project

Officially: what is the essence of E40 waterway restoration project and what do the government organizations of Belarus think about it.
